{"tid":1862494,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有無人同我一樣如果社區大爆發都支持醫護繼續罷工？","createTime":"2020-02-04T15:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T18:32:07.000Z","uid":13388,"like":142,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"4055a120e38c3e7d132ecf2e18b2eb0936a1f727","tid":1862494,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:50:38.000Z","msg":"我就咁諗<br />\n呢次真係黃金機會<br />\n呢家就係鬥人性最低處<br />\n柒婆就已經拋開一切<br />\n所以我地無得唔同佢鬥<br />\n<br />\n我touch wood講句<br />\n中左既話<br />\n除左去狗屋之外<br />\n仲會拍片叫班醫護咪撚救我<br />\n要佢地繼續罷工<br />\n<br />\n因為呢句七個月前都講過<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n唔係因為希望先堅持<br />\n而係堅持而有希望呀<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n知唔知呀各位香港罷工既醫護手足<br />\n<br />\n求下你地唔好放棄罷工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：小弟同公司有係廣告界罷工<br />\n大家都支持你地<br />\n<br />\n唔該正評同推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54edac3658b58ec2f58561deefdf0805d7605b7","tid":1862494,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:54:12.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"7dff822bc8fc8330bafbdd3095f2be5d10cc712a","tid":1862494,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:54:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n唔係因為希望有堅持<br />\n而係堅持先有希望<br />\n<br />\n</span></spa